Game.....: Dragonriders - Chronicles Of Pern
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: August 8th, 2001
Ripped.......: FMV Downsampled

Play as D'Kor as you search to find a queen for your homeland: Pern. After the sudden death of the previous queen, it is imperative for D'Kor to find a replacement, and soon. A deadly disease is spreading throughout his homeland, weakening the populace and killing many of the dragon riders, the world's only defense against the recurring Threads, which rain on the planet once every 200 years.